{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_04_01_short",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 未知の体験 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――とある日の午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.2066666762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんはライブを中心に活動しているけど\nライブ以外の仕事はどう思っているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san mainly focuses on live performances‚\nbut what do you think about other types of work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私はライブパフォーマンスでファンのみなさんに\n楽しんでもらうことがアイドルの本分だと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe that the main duty of an idol is to entertain\nthe fans through live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、トリエルの知名度が上がるのなら\n苦手な仕事に挑戦することもやぶさかではありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ if it helps raise TRINITYAiLE's popularity‚\nI'm willing to challenge jobs I'm not good at.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でもこれはやりたくないという線引きはあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you have any types of work you really don't want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "明確な線引きはありません。今までしたことがなかった\n水着グラビアも星見プロに来て解禁しましたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is no clear line. I haven't done anything like that before.\nI even did a swimsuit gravure shoot after coming to Hoshimi Production…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時は苦労を掛けてすまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry for causing you trouble back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい\n{user}さんのことは信頼していますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't worry about it.\nI trust you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが取ってきた仕事なら\n間違いはないと信じています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's a job {user}-san bring me‚\nI believe there won't be any mistakes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5645600924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえるのは嬉しいが、責任重大だな……\n実は天動さんに新しい仕事のオファーがきてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's reassuring to hear that‚ but the responsibility is significant…\nActually‚ there's a new job offer for you‚ Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}